{"url": "https://morningstaronline.co.uk/article/eurostar-staff-suspend-industrial-ballot-after-securing-olympics-bonus", "uid": "morningstaronline.co.uk-article-eurostar-staff-suspend-industrial-ballot-after-securing-olympics-bonus", "images": ["https://morningstaronline.co.uk/sites/default/files/styles/wide/public/2025-06/Morning%20Star%20website%20banner%201350x170%20copy.png.webp?itok=KO4d_mHo", "https://morningstaronline.co.uk/sites/default/files/styles/desktop/public/Eurostar%20olympics.jpg.webp?itok=YpQAs4sg", "https://morningstaronline.co.uk/sites/default/files/styles/wide/public/2024-11/Donate%20to%20the%20Fighting%20Fund.jpg.webp?itok=KBHrRFwU", "https://morningstaronline.co.uk/sites/default/files/styles/wide/public/2025-05/Donate%20to%20the%2095%20Years%20Fund.jpg.webp?itok=qVG3CIbF", "https://morningstaronline.co.uk/sites/default/files/styles/wide/public/2025-05/The%2095th%20Anniversary%20Appeal.jpg.webp?itok=JbmYWD7p"], "publication-date": "", "text": "TRANSPORT union RMT secured improved payments for Eurostar staff working the Olympic games following intense negotiations and a ballot for industrial action.\n\nEurostar had initially proposed a shift-based payment system, which RMT rejected as divisive and insufficient.\n\nThe rail company has now agreed to provide a one-off bonus instead, averting the threat of industrial action during what is expected to be a busy period.", "title": "Eurostar staff suspend industrial ballot after securing Olympics bonus | Morning Star", "top-image": "https://morningstaronline.co.uk/sites/default/files/styles/wide/public/2025-06/Morning%20Star%20website%20banner%201350x170%20copy.png.webp?itok=KO4d_mHo", "domain": "morningstaronline.co.uk", "lang": "en", "author": "", "description": "", "keywords": ""}